  <summary>7/26/2006--Introduced.
Calls on: (1) all parties in the Middle East to observe a cease-fire and renew peace efforts; and (2) the United States and the international community to assist in reconstruction efforts in violence-affected areas of the Middle East. Urges all parties to recognize Israel's right to exist.</summary>
